
<div class="section-heading">
  <div class="container">
  <h1>Invest in Our Restaurant</h1>
  <p>Thank you for your interest in investing in our restaurant. We are excited about the opportunity to grow and expand, and we welcome investors who share our vision.</p>
  <p>To learn more about investment opportunities, please fill out the form below and our team will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>

  <div class="contact-form">
    <h2>Contact Form</h2>
    <form action="/investor-inquiry" method="POST">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Full Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Enter your phone number" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="company">Company / Organization</label>
        <input type="text" id="company" name="company" placeholder="Enter your company or organization name">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="role">Role</label>
        <input type="text" id="role" name="role" placeholder="Enter your role or title">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="investment">Investment Amount (USD)</label>
        <input type="number" id="investment" name="investment" placeholder="Enter the amount you're considering to invest" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="message">Message / Additional Information</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Enter any message or additional information"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
